@startuml pcard-annual-audit-current
title P-Card Annual Audit Process (Current - To Be Replaced)

skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FFF8F0
skinparam activityBorderColor #B44646

|Procurement Services|
start
:Send audit memo, audit form,\nand agency spreadsheet\nto each agency;

|Agency / Department Head|
:Receive audit documents;
:Verify cardholder and\napprover listing;

if (Changes needed?) then (no)
  :Check "listing is correct"\non audit form;
  :Sign and date form;
else (yes)
  :Highlight changes in\nbright color on spreadsheet;
  :Sign and date audit form;
  :Attach updated spreadsheet;
endif

:Return form (and spreadsheet\nif changes) to Geraldine\nvia email;

|Procurement Services|
:Receive completed audit;
:Process any requested changes;
:Update P-Card inventory;
stop

note right
  **Pain Points (to automate in Paperboy):**
  - Manual email-based process
  - Paper/PDF forms and spreadsheets
  - Relies on annual cycle instead of real-time
  - No tracking of response status
end note

@enduml
